 Frontiers North Adventures has provided us with a dedicated vehicle to meet our needs and objectives 

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:37.000
 It is used by the International Polar Preservation Organization as a mobile broadcasting studio 

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:43.000
 We are really happy to share our resources 

00:03:43.500 --> 00:03:50.500
 So that Polar Polar International can deliver its message from the Tundra region around Churchill to people around the world 

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:58.000
 And awareness of the importance of better understanding the impacts of climate change on polar bears in the Arctic. 

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:06.000
 We have a lot of awareness and education campaigns and one of the most important campaigns we are conducting now is Tundra Connections. 

00:04:06.330 --> 00:04:11.000
 So that students learn more about polar bears, prompting them to help and take action. 

