 Now, we want to show you something, there is a polar bear outside our window 

00:04:20.500 --> 00:04:22.000
 It's coming to greet you guys. 

00:04:24.500 --> 00:04:27.500
 Children are dazzled the first time they see the polar bear on the camera 

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:31.000
 "Look there's a polar bear!" Or are very excited 

00:04:31.330 --> 00:04:35.000
 It is really wonderful that we can bring this experience to them. 

