 The fact that this beautiful big white bear may disappear completely within 50-60 years 

00:05:12.330 --> 00:05:15.750
 The fact that polar bears are major species, at the top of the food chain. 

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:18.000
 Without it, everything else collapses. 

